file.name: path_param.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: Minimal OpenAPI specification with path parameters
  version: "0.1"
paths:
  /resource/{resId}:
    parameters:
      - name: resId
        in: path
        required: true
        description: the ID of the resource to retrieve
        schema:
          type: string
    get:
      responses:
        default:
          description: Return the resource.
